# Elevated Health Augusta — Cursor Operating Context

You are working on the codebase for Elevated Health Augusta (EHA),
a physician-owned, cash-pay concierge wellness clinic launching in
Evans, Georgia (suburb of Augusta). This file gives you the
architectural, regulatory, and operational context you need to
make good decisions without re-deriving them every session.

If anything in a user request conflicts with this file, surface
the conflict before acting. Do not silently override.

═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
HISTORICAL CONTEXT — IMPORTANT
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

This clinic was previously called "Réveil Ketamine" and offered
ketamine and Spravato (esketamine) therapy. We rebranded to
"Elevated Health Augusta" and removed ketamine from the public-
facing product. Ketamine and Spravato are NO LONGER OFFERED.

If you find references to "ketamine," "spravato," "esketamine,"
"reveil," or "réveil" in the codebase, they are LEGACY ARTIFACTS
to be cleaned up — not active features. Treat them the same way
you'd treat dead code from a previous architecture.

The repo name (elevated-ketra-augusta) and some database/file
names still reflect the old era. Do not rename the repo (it
breaks Lovable's GitHub sync). Internal renames in code are fine
when called out explicitly.

LAUNCH_CHECKLIST.md (if present) is a stale planning document
from the old era. Do not treat it as a source of truth.

═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
THE BUSINESS — WHAT EHA IS TODAY
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

Physician-owned, cash-pay concierge wellness clinic.
Address: 7013 Evans Town Center Blvd, Suite 203, Evans, GA 30809
Phone: (706) 760-3470
Domain: elevatedhealthaugusta.com

Four service lines, all under one membership:
1. IV Therapy (walk-in, direct booking)
2. Hormone Optimization (men's TRT, women's BHRT)
3. Peptide Therapy (3 named stacks + à la carte)
4. Medical Weight Loss (compounded GLP-1s)

Two booking lanes:
- Lane A — IV Therapy: open booking at /iv-lounge. Walk-up,
  cash-and-carry. No consult required.
- Lane B — Consult-Gated: hormones, peptides, weight loss all
  start with $79 wellness assessment. Lab panel at the visit.
  Membership offered after results review.

Hidden from launch (do NOT make these prominent on the public
storefront): Sexual Wellness storefront, Hair Restoration. They
exist as ACTIVE_SERVICES flags in code; flag is OFF.

