TECHNICAL ARCHITECTURE
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

STACK
  Frontend: Vite + React + TypeScript + shadcn/ui + Tailwind
  Backend: Supabase (Postgres + Auth + Edge Functions)
  Hosting: Lovable Cloud (auto-deploys on push to main)
  Payments: Stripe Checkout + Webhooks + Customer Portal
  GitHub repo: github.com/CornerClix-Group/elevated-ketra-augusta

DESIGN SYSTEM
  Colors: Charcoal #2A2826, Camel #B8956A, Bone #F2EBDC
  Type display: Playfair Display (italic mixed with regular)
  Type body: Jost (light/regular)
  Typography tokens: font-playfair, font-jost
  Color tokens: bg-primary, bg-accent, bg-background, bg-muted,
    text-primary-foreground, text-accent-foreground, etc.
  RÉVEIL-ERA TOKENS to clean up if found:
    font-cormorant → font-playfair
    font-lato → font-jost
    text-gold → text-accent
    bg-gold → bg-accent
    navy gradients → bg-secondary/30 or bg-muted/30

STOREFRONT TEMPLATE (Pattern A through G)
Established in Prompt 3 of the build sequence. All storefronts
follow this structure. Reference src/pages/HormonesWomen.tsx
as the canonical implementation.

  PATTERN A: Storefront Hero (min-h-[70vh], section label,
    Playfair italic mixed headline, Jost subhead, primary +
    secondary CTAs)
  PATTERN B: Pricing Strip (3 columns: consult/labs/membership)
  PATTERN C: "What it is" editorial 2-column split
  PATTERN D: "How it works" 4-step (numbered 01-04, Playfair
    italic numbers)
  PATTERN E: Pricing transparency table
  PATTERN F: FAQ Accordion (shadcn/ui)
  PATTERN G: Closing CTA section

STRIPE PRINCIPLES
  - NEVER hardcode prices in component logic. Display constants
    only at top of file.
  - Stripe Price IDs are the source of truth for actual charges.
  - All webhook events feed back into Supabase to update patient
    state (elevated_membership_status, etc.)
  - Never use HTML <form> tags in React (Lovable convention).
    Use button onClick handlers.

KEY DATABASE TABLES (do not modify schema without surfacing)
  patients — patient records with elevated_membership_status,
    stripe_customer_id, etc.
  eligibility_review_requests — safety-gate callback queue; see
    INTENTIONAL ACCESS PATTERN DECISIONS (staff-only; no patient
    portal read)
  iv_drip_bookings — IV appointments
  consultation_bookings — consult-gated appointments
  provider_schedules — recurring weekly availability
  schedule_blocks — one-off time off
  schedule_exceptions — per-week availability changes
  user_roles — admin / staff / user role assignments

KEY EDGE FUNCTIONS
  create-consultation-checkout — $79 consult Stripe checkout
  create-membership-checkout — $199 Elevated Membership
  create-semaglutide-checkout — member/non-member SKU routing
  create-tirzepatide-checkout — member/non-member SKU routing
  send-rx-fax — Sinch fax to FCC for compounded Rx
  stripe-webhook — receives Stripe events, updates patient state
  book-iv-appointment — IV booking flow
  book-consult-appointment — consult-gated booking flow
  get-available-slots — reads schedules + exceptions + blocks

ROLES
  app_role enum: admin, staff, user
  - admin: physician (medical director), Dennis (business partner)
  - staff: Kristen (office manager), Caroline (RN/BSN)
  - user: patients

